| 17e4915a-ada0-4b95-bacf-ba67133f39a7 | leap                   | active |
+--------------------------------------+------------------------+--------+
     </screen>
    </step>
    <step>
     <para>
      Check the details of the image
     </para>
     <screen>
&prompt.ardana;openstack image show 17e4915a-ada0-4b95-bacf-ba67133f39a7
     </screen>
